Who We Defend
J. Haskins Law provides professional license defense to individuals across various fields, including:
Healthcare Professionals: Doctors, Nurse Practitioners, Physician Assistants, Dentists, Pharmacists, and other healthcare providers who face accusations of malpractice, substandard care, or ethical violations.
Realtors & Financial Advisors: Real estate agents and financial professionals accused of fraud, misrepresentation, or breaches of fiduciary duty.
General Contractors: Defending against complaints of negligence, improper practices, or failure to comply with state or local regulations.
Architects & Engineers: Professionals facing accusations of misconduct, incompetence, or violations of state licensure regulations.
When your license and livelihood are on the line, you need a team that understands your industry and has the expertise to fight for you. At J. Haskins Law, we bring years of experience across multiple professions to help you navigate these complex and stressful situations.

